thread.title: Ice sculpture artists cut their finest at international design contest

title: Ice sculpture artists cut their finest at international design contest
text:
Ice sculpture artists cut their finest at international design contest 2:25pm GMT - 01:32 
Over 60 participants from 14 different countries competed in an international ice sculpture contest in northern China, pulling blocks from a local river. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
